Load balancer that routes messages to the same endpoint based on a correlation expression, ensuring session affinity
]]>
      </xs:documentation>
    </xs:annotation>
  </xs:element>
  <xs:element name="stop" type="tns:stopDefinition">
    <xs:annotation>
      <xs:documentation xml:lang="en">
